"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Trading platform eToro will be limiting crypto assets cardano (ADA) and tron (TRX) for U.S. customers starting in December due to “business-related considerations in the evolving regulatory environment,” according to a [statement](https://www.etoro.com/en-us/news-and-analysis/etoro-updates/important-update-regarding-ada-and-trx/) on its website.\\n\\n* The statement, published Tuesday, said that users in the U.S. will “no longer be able to open new positions in, or receive staking rewards for,” ADA and TRX.\\n* Restrictions on opening new positions in ADA and TRX will take effect on Dec. 26, while staking for these assets will end on Dec. 31, the statement said.\\n* The final staking rewards payout for both assets will take place on Jan. 15, 2022.\\n* According to eToro’s announcement, users will still be able to “securely hold existing positions” for the two cryptocurrencies, as the limitations only apply to new positions.\\n* Users can sell their ADA or TRX in exchange for U.S. dollars anytime, and eToro is working on a way to make it possible for users to move these two assets to their eToro crypto wallets, the statement said.\\n* Since the announcement was published, at one point, [ADA](https://www.coindesk.com/price/cardano/) prices [dropped](https://www.ibtimes.com/ada-plunges-after-etoro-limits-users-opening-new-cardano-tron-positions-3344203) by more than 6%. At press time, [TRX](https://www.coindesk.com/price/tron/) was down 2.4%.\\n* Taking to [Twitter](https://twitter.com/IOHK_Charles/status/1463282188128980997) on Tuesday, Cardano founder Charles Hoskinson said eToro’s decision was due to a “systemic lack of clarity” in global crypto regulations.\",\"timestamp\":1637805987,\"title\":\"EToro to Limit Cardano and Tron for US Customers, Coin Prices Fall\"},\"digest\":\"_eqGNj02RxIzWh8TTan6i-YGZ8EhYUw1WUsJOtF7rGQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4FA4167b3C94A80416bBc768fB919BF3AcE9F8C2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"B_KWwC36LhSIj1UKfxSq66vEgnbOvrYvqsnj2YqrI9c\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"R3ZjJFf4EyJ9jXGTUqrQMvvi9uzVInjxD0cMFyDSWGk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3rZRKyf_rpyNSTxcP_F4-dRX5XOR5wIux0779qXObjXLRUpcXaYJkVjNu1HvhMchAr6Qk6ce3G9IvhupGmuIoQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5f595cd3cb2fc0953a4809f42613fb57147c2f65f06637c0acee4fb8b8a5c02c0efd8dafdd1812ecc671ee4f4b2d0c72cccbb377b98cc167148a0fb4ec4766a01b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"B_KWwC36LhSIj1UKfxSq66vEgnbOvrYvqsnj2YqrI9c\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"R3ZjJFf4EyJ9jXGTUqrQMvvi9uzVInjxD0cMFyDSWGk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"_eqGNj02RxIzWh8TTan6i-YGZ8EhYUw1WUsJOtF7rGQ\"}"